[recv] {"type": "turn_end", "message": {"role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "thinking", "thinking": "**Exploring class loading**\n\nI’m considering how the URLClassLoader treats classes loaded from JAR files as resources. It's interesting to think about how we can override resource methods in this context. There's also the potential issue with dynamic class loading, especially with native images. I'm curious if a dynamically loaded class could conflict if it's already on the classpath and how that interacts with using a custom loader. If the class is known and the image has the bytecode, what happens then?", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_01fca2c762ffb37f0169f1130e29548190bdbce37494de6a15\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp8RMf7wrtlKCjdCdC7YAUj10ot2fdiTdi4sEh8U6XxsNCyNzWrjPsN2No6wlIKeuvjnXYgddLf5pkQBpuFt495ggfHXqBH9sZD8jwRP-csYETAicyUM1VpfDB4fCFKBJ10K8U66fxw5x3O-hc1jIedtIpnoqQDMUYrbarB1SJZcKWGNsZtAw4BMUVHljEmiq_OvENtqw4ZNm9NfY6F_RBctSkKkPQFBBm9kEwUhkCgRynsdcJPB6Ke_HW1fiT72_FM6iyuI2YgAPR-bSh1XirWS5HTqUFmJU5wKSFAvZc1R8b7d3Sz83PBjD3hDWL51iFZ1swlyiYkdm5NGIW1SG7pVrc7M-R-SLtnOo40zDRmQnigtHytqzy7A_xj3QtyUVCu11TVUGAPvd9MTilsP7HKGF3k2CpH2WOBS8OmE1GmuJnUE8oQVMYcJMGuYV0FANZch5CzLSVSoi2TZ9e7JH-7K7nwdqAW8iA_6TXlBR-a9GA8X9Z05pXWcOsiEOd8KGRO5wLDPTOkAjqnelrZhoVE5P0wDJGV8h0yzf7Z3PEUE_CU4KrqVk9eXEAwiBjSiGtxyi5DajaEUCWUjstzSn-8DdS1G6n4PogTwHCP7zVPAjhi5kYVhmCicjpF_jJYz_1ZBQZZjRmkXP00-w-FNCJT9_89S1_-pBYYbsvHiRnUmTo9NOljuJmQUp9gZeJTog60Wh5Ww9h-iRubIOHnsahGwe6jY6iZ0Oe11_HwCzxi5og2121r5zDkgLz8GomFks1inSb0ME1Kh9djHA0lcaYt9Orw4IjW3wvG6rBv3Hiri53vl8EnnleAXSuu00INJGNQRO7t8EUJnEjd0UIUewbsKeZmoplhECJLYt5u7sKB_1QyeOFN2pOLB7p-DhR-3Mwpng9Krufgan4y3Do7C9FNd8P5clnjdRxWAnQAbEI4px8Ev4mz9q21mR1WJU3g-E_0AY8x2eyA699djP8aapMns9peRPeOTySDPAqjaqId1VLI-w9KSdx9WXovCaLPpWOxG9BeubM6mR7WvP4aLDoKXIXAN5i69f7hSUTYsaiL9mtrXg1cmq927CmU3kGjcSnDbQThz13YgDcxpplXcvc_YWD8ZjF1SvmQLqcVsyT_43T5bdRVjah9cFTjiql960ENC7avG_41NwImMK1pbTKhWaIy9khj53h6hxmHYQt6KCf7beMzBkMFRnfUs1RdTsDtdKU24a_GEp_fv1ogUz